<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE DEFEATED 1 ALBAHERON.</b></font>

10
00:02:19,750 --> 00:02:23,130
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}YOU HAVE GAINED 100 EXP.</b></font>

11
00:02:20,750 --> 00:02:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, man...</font>

12
00:02:23,210 --> 00:02:26,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I WOOOOON!</font>

13
00:02:28,380 --> 00:02:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I beat my first monster!</font>

14
00:02:30,750 --> 00:02:33,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is giving me a rush beyond words!</font>

15
00:02:35,080 --> 00:02:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">An albaheron?!</font>

16
00:02:36,750 --> 00:02:37,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Look what I got!</font>

17
00:02:38,420 --> 00:02:39,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How did you manage that?!</font>

18
00:02:39,920 --> 00:02:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It happened to land nearby,
so I took it by surprise!</font>

19
00:02:43,420 --> 00:02:45,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's mostly true.</font>

20
00:02:45,710 --> 00:02:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're amazing, Allen!</font>

21
00:02:48,250 --> 00:02:49,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's scawy!</font>

22
00:02:49,630 --> 00:02:52,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't worry, Mash. It won't move or anything.</font>

23
00:02:52,960 --> 00:02:57,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey. You've got a cut on your cheek.
Are you hurt anywhere else?</font>

24
00:02:57,210 --> 00:02:59,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The bleeding stopped already. I'm fine!</font>

25
00:02:59,710 --> 00:03:04,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is real impressive, kid. You took it down
with your wooden sword and some rocks?</font>

26
00:03:04,290 --> 00:03:04,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yep!</font>

27
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:07,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh, I see some dog-like bite marks here.</font>

28
00:03:07,960 --> 00:03:08,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?!</font>

29
00:03:08,630 --> 00:03:09,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Did you bite it, Allen?</font>

30
00:03:09,960 --> 00:03:10,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh crap!</font>

31
00:03:11,210 --> 00:03:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I-I'm not sure, I was fighting on pure instinct...</font>

32
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Chomp! Chomp! Chomp! Chomp! Chomp! Chomp!</font>

33
00:03:14,670 --> 00:03:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ow! Ow! Ow!</font>

34
00:03:19,960 --> 00:03:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, right.</font>

35
00:03:21,330 --> 00:03:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Rodin. I'll bleed it out for ya.</font>

36
00:03:23,670 --> 00:03:25,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks. Please do.</font>

37
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:29,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow! That's one big lump.</font>

38
00:03:30,880 --> 00:03:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bet he got that while playing knights with Krena.</font>

39
00:03:33,290 --> 00:03:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gerda must be slow on his feet.</font>

40
00:03:37,420 --> 00:03:38,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, Allen.</font>

41
00:03:38,710 --> 00:03:40,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lend me a hand.</font>

42
00:03:41,880 --> 00:03:44,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Albaherons weigh 60 kilos on average.</font>

43
00:03:44,580 --> 00:03:47,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That drops to 20 kilos after you
drain the blood and dry 'em out.</font>

44
00:03:47,830 --> 00:03:49,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Only half of that is edible meat, though.</font>

45
00:03:50,290 --> 00:03:51,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Their wings fetch a pretty penny, too.</font>

46
00:03:52,330 --> 00:03:55,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm happy he's willing to teach me all this!</font>

47
00:03:55,420 --> 00:03:59,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Though, we still gotta fork over
most of it to the upper class.</font>

48
00:03:59,290 --> 00:04:04,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? The sixty percent tax
even applies to wild monsters?</font>

49
00:04:04,250 --> 00:04:05,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yep.</font>

50
00:04:05,170 --> 00:04:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're nice enough to overlook
smaller ones like E-rank horned rabbits.</font>

51
00:04:08,630 --> 00:04:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But albaherons are D-rank.</font>

52
00:04:11,380 --> 00:04:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What a bum deal.</font>

53
00:04:13,420 --> 00:04:14,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One more thing.</font>

54
00:04:15,130 --> 00:04:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Almost... got it!</font>

55
00:04:18,330 --> 00:04:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is a magic stone.</font>

56
00:04:19,790 --> 00:04:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh yeah?</font>

57
00:04:21,290 --> 00:04:24,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Magic stones from any monster
above D-rank fall under the tax.</font>

58
00:04:24,540 --> 00:04:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No biggie, though.
They're worthless to us in the village anyways.</font>

59
00:04:30,000 --> 00:04:31,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But listen!</font>

60
00:04:31,420 --> 00:04:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A kid like you wouldn't be out there catching
monsters if your dad hadn't gotten hurt so bad.</font>

61
00:04:37,210 --> 00:04:40,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We can use that as leverage
to negotiate a bigger cut with the chieftain.</font>

62
00:04:40,380 --> 00:04:41,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, I see.</font>

63
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think I have an idea, Mister Gerda!</font>

64
00:04:45,040 --> 00:04:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whisper, whisper, whisper.</font>

65
00:04:48,500 --> 00:04:51,830
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}CHIEFTAIN'S RESIDENCE</b></font>

66
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, there you have it.</font>

67
00:04:52,000 --> 00:04:56,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Rodin's youngster stuck his little neck out
to nab this monster.</font>

68
00:04:56,540 --> 00:04:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ah, I see! Wonderful!</font>

69
00:04:58,670 --> 00:04:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here's the deal.</font>

70
00:04:59,580 --> 00:05:00,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

71
00:05:00,460 --> 00:05:02,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We'll fork over the entirety of its wings as tax.</font>

72
00:05:03,000 --> 00:05:05,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But you don't mind us taking the rest, yeah?</font>

73
00:05:05,420 --> 00:05:08,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ah, I see. Wonder-fuh?</font>

74
00:05:08,130 --> 00:05:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">C'mon. That's not such a big deal, is it?</font>

75
00:05:10,040 --> 00:05:11,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, wait, wait!</font>

76
00:05:11,670 --> 00:05:13,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's a problem!</font>

77
00:05:13,540 --> 00:05:17,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The baron has asked that we deliver
even more meat this year, you see.</font>

78
00:05:17,880 --> 00:05:20,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You understand what that means, right?</font>

79
00:05:20,250 --> 00:05:21,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? The baron did?</font>

80
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is that why the chief was so insistent
on having commoners join the hunt?</font>

81
00:05:25,420 --> 00:05:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You drive a hard bargain.</font>

82
00:05:27,040 --> 00:05:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fine, we'll throw in
the magic stone, too. How's that?</font>

83
00:05:29,670 --> 00:05:32,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Just the wings and the magic stone?</font>

84
00:05:32,380 --> 00:05:37,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, shucks! If only SOMEBODY
hadn't asked the impossible of us.</font>

85
00:05:37,170 --> 00:05:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then maybe our resident hero, Rodin,
wouldn't have gotten hurt so badly.</font>

86
00:05:39,960 --> 00:05:42,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now his poor family is on the verge
of starving to death.</font>

87
00:05:42,670 --> 00:05:45,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">How can they survive the winter
with four mouths to feed?</font>

88
00:05:45,000 --> 00:05:47,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh! I'm so hungry!</font>

89
00:05:48,630 --> 00:05:49,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's making me dizzy...</font>

90
00:05:49,460 --> 00:05:52,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh no, Allen! Hang in there!</font>

91
00:05:52,130 --> 00:05:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Heavens me! Just WHO can we blame
for this awful predicament?</font>

92
00:05:56,130 --> 00:05:58,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, all right! I get it!</font>

93
00:05:58,540 --> 00:06:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I do owe a lot to Rodin for his work.
I suppose you can have it.</font>

94
00:06:04,920 --> 00:06:07,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Boom, baby! That's how we do it!</font>

95
00:06:07,880 --> 00:06:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, chief!</font>

96
00:06:11,330 --> 00:06:12,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Don't mention it...</font>

97
00:06:14,330 --> 00:06:19,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, in the future, we can keep the meat and just
give you the wings and magic stones, right?</font>

98
00:06:19,710 --> 00:06:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?!</font>

99
00:06:20,920 --> 00:06:23,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is the real crux of the issue!</font>

100
00:06:23,380 --> 00:06:25,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Come now, Allen!</font>

101
00:06:25,080 --> 00:06:28,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's not good to count your albaherons
