102
00:06:28,790 --> 00:06:32,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They're tough to get. Right, chief?</font>

103
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:35,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Way to sell him on it!</font>

104
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's a good point.</font>

105
00:06:37,540 --> 00:06:42,000
