00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}SUMMONS AVAILABLE FOR CREATION:</b></font>

172
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}INSECTS: FGH, BEASTS: FGH, BIRDS: FG, PLANTS: F</b></font>

173
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}INVENTORY:</b></font>

174
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}INSECTS F 2 COPIES, G 3 COPIES</b></font>

175
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}BEASTS F 16 COPIES</b></font>

176
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}BIRDS F 2 COPIES</b></font>

177
00:08:13,170 --> 00:08:17,290
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}PLANT F 7 COPIES</b></font>

178
00:08:13,460 --> 00:08:15,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">of the level up yet.</font>

179
00:08:15,580 --> 00:08:16,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's rough.</font>

180
00:08:17,920 --> 00:08:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, whatever.</font>

181
00:08:19,330 --> 00:08:22,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes! Hell yes! I did it!</font>

182
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}HP HAS GONE UP BY 25</b></font>

183
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}MP HAS GONE UP BY 40</b></font>

184
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}ATTACK HAS GONE UP BY 14</b></font>

185
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}ENDURANCE HAS GONE UP BY 14</b></font>

186
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}AGILITY HAS GONE UP BY 26</b></font>

187
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}INTELLIGENCE HAS GONE UP BY 40</b></font>

188
00:08:22,460 --> 00:08:31,420
<font size="27" color="#f4f1e8"><b>{\an7}LUCK HAS GONE UP BY 26</b></font>

189
00:08:22,580 --> 00:08:24,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I leveled up!</font>

190
00:08:28,670 --> 00:08:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Alright! Those are big gains!</font>

191
00:08:31,540 --> 00:08:32,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Bring it in.</font>

192
00:08:33,750 --> 00:08:35,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Six years after being reincarnated.</font>

193
00:08:35,710 --> 00:08:37,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've finally hit my first level up.</font>

194
00:08:38,330 --> 00:08:41,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So this is what it's like to pass
a "Trial of the Gods", huh?</font>

195
00:08:41,920 --> 00:08:43,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feels amazing.</font>

196
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It might be time that I
let the fam in on the truth.</font>

197
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm home!</font>

198
00:08:52,460 --> 00:08:53,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, welcome back.</font>

199
00:08:53,920 --> 00:08:56,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa! You caught two of them today?!</font>

200
00:08:56,960 --> 00:09:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yep! I actually beat them at the same time.
Pretty amazing, huh?</font>

201
00:09:00,750 --> 00:09:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Wait a sec, Allen...</font>

202
00:09:02,540 --> 00:09:03,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is it?</font>

203
00:09:05,080 --> 00:09:06,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Never mind. It's nothing.</font>

204
00:09:08,210 --> 00:09:09,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ah! I gotta go!</font>

205
00:09:14,540 --> 00:09:17,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">With today's hunt,
I've met my goal of 10 monsters.</font>

206
00:09:17,460 --> 00:09:20,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Once I dry the meat,
we'll have enough to make it through winter!</font>

207
00:09:22,210 --> 00:09:24,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only thing left now is to trade for firewood!</font>

208
00:09:26,540 --> 00:09:29,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Since there are a lot of albaherons around
for migration season,</font>

209
00:09:29,460 --> 00:09:31,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I could try to hit level three by hunting 20 more.</font>

210
00:09:32,080 --> 00:09:33,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But that'll be hard to do
before the end of the year.</font>

211
00:09:35,170 --> 00:09:35,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

212
00:09:36,880 --> 00:09:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ow!</font>

213
00:09:38,420 --> 00:09:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">See ya tomorrow!</font>

214
00:09:47,880 --> 00:09:49,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, you wanted to talk with us?</font>

215
00:09:50,170 --> 00:09:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah. This might throw you for a loop, but...</font>

216
00:09:53,670 --> 00:09:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">to tell the truth, I heard an oracle from God
back when I was one year old.</font>

217
00:09:58,460 --> 00:09:59,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">An oracle?</font>

218
00:09:59,790 --> 00:10:01,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you talking about Lord Elmea?</font>

219
00:10:01,880 --> 00:10:02,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's right.</font>

220
00:10:04,040 --> 00:10:08,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">"Young Allen. I shall bless you
with power and wisdom."</font>

221
00:10:08,750 --> 00:10:09,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So he said!</font>

222
00:10:10,920 --> 00:10:13,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is that supposed to mean, exactly?</font>

223
00:10:13,460 --> 00:10:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It basically means I'm smarter
and physically stronger than your average person.</font>

224
00:10:18,790 --> 00:10:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But at the same time...</font>

225
00:10:20,540 --> 00:10:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">"You shall be faced with trials beyond
what even a hundred men could accomplish."</font>

226
00:10:25,380 --> 00:10:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">"Use your blessings of power
and wisdom to overcome them."</font>

227
00:10:29,170 --> 00:10:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, yeah!</font>

228
00:10:30,130 --> 00:10:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A hundred men?!</font>

229
00:10:31,790 --> 00:10:34,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, Lord! How could you do this to my Allen?!</font>

230
00:10:34,880 --> 00:10:40,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I see. You must have bested
one of those trials today, huh?</font>

231
00:10:40,540 --> 00:10:44,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You probably haven't noticed, but the cut you had
on your cheek this morning has disappeared.</font>

232
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Oh...</font>

233
00:10:48,170 --> 00:10:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I know what it's like to pass a Trial of the Gods.</font>

234
00:10:50,540 --> 00:10:52,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I figured that's what happened with you.</font>

235
00:10:52,540 --> 00:10:53,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh yeah?</font>

236
00:10:53,960 --> 00:10:57,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, but what about your results
from last year's Appraisal Ceremony?</font>

237
00:10:57,000 --> 00:11:00,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I got another oracle from Elmea
about that a couple months ago.</font>

238
00:11:00,580 --> 00:11:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Jeez, that recently?!
But wait a minute, show proper respect!</font>

239
00:11:04,420 --> 00:11:06,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's LORD Elmea to you, got it?</font>

240
00:11:06,130 --> 00:11:09,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sure, I'll be careful from now on.</font>

241
00:11:09,540 --> 00:11:10,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good.</font>

242
00:11:11,040 --> 00:11:13,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The reason my attributes were ranked so low
at the Appraisal Ceremony</font>

243
00:11:13,960 --> 00:11:17,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">is because they take the slower progression
of my trials into account.</font>

244
00:11:17,670 --> 00:11:19,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And the reason I was judged not to have a talent</font>

245
00:11:19,380 --> 00:11:22,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">is because mine was actually
too new to be recognized.</font>

246
00:11:22,630 --> 00:11:25,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wait, so you DO have a talent?</font>

247
00:11:25,630 --> 00:11:26,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What kind is it?</font>

248
00:11:27,000 --> 00:11:29,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, he never told me what it was...</font>

249
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shoot.</font>

250
00:11:32,250 --> 00:11:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Sorry, Dad. I can't say anything
about being a Summoner yet.</font>

251
00:11:36,710 --> 00:11:39,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm worried some people
might get the wrong idea</font>

252
00:11:39,130 --> 00:11:41,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">if they find out I can summon
and control creatures.</font>

253
00:11:42,130 --> 00:11:44,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And naturally, I can't tell anybody
that I was reincarnated.</font>

254
00:11:46,500 --> 00:11:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, Allen! I wish you would have told us sooner!</font>

255
00:11:49,960 --> 00:11:53,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Your habit of throwing
those rocks at trees every day,</font>

256
00:11:53,920 --> 00:11:56,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">and now hunting these big monsters,</font>

257
00:11:56,500 --> 00:11:59,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">it's because you've been fighting
to overcome the Lord's trial, huh?</font>

258
00:11:59,250 --> 00:12:00,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And all by yourself!</font>

259
00:12:00,920 --> 00:12:02,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm sorry, Mom.</font>

260
00:12:04,790 --> 00:12:05,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You little dummy.</font>

261
00:12:07,040 --> 00:12:08,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So, what are you going to do now?</font>

262
00:12:09,250 --> 00:12:09,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well...</font>

263
00:12:10,420 --> 00:12:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I want to prove myself worthy
by passing the trials.</font>

264
00:12:13,420 --> 00:12:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So I'll be brave and take them head-on.</font>

265
00:12:15,880 --> 00:12:18,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">All right. I figured as much.</font>

266
00:12:19,380 --> 00:12:22,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Lord Elmea prepared this challenge
specifically for you.</font>

267
00:12:23,250 --> 00:12:24,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It's worth taking up the gauntlet.</font>

268
00:12:25,540 --> 00:12:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And if you run into trouble,
don't hesitate to ask for our help.</font>

269
00:12:29,000 --> 00:12:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay.</font>

270
00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:33,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks so much! Dad, Mom!</font>

271
00:12:33,880 --> 00:12:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, Allen? Keep this all between us for now.</font>

272
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It would be bad if anyone took you
for a false prophet.</font>

273
00:12:40,960 --> 00:12:43,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But... do you mind if I tell Gerda?</font>

274
00:12:43,630 --> 00:12:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? Sure, that's fine with me.</font>

275
00:12:45,670 --> 00:12:47,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, great!</font>

276
00:12:47,330 --> 00:12:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He's always bragging about
how Krena's a Sword Lord and all.</font>

277
00:12:50,580 --> 00:12:53,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now I can tell him that my son
is just as incredible!</font>

278
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:58,960
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}THE HARDCORE GAMER DOMINATES</b></font>

279
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:58,960
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}IN ANOTHER WORLD WITH GARBAGE BALANCING</b></font>

280
00:12:59,540 --> 00:13:01,920
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}ALLEN - AGE 6</b></font>

281
00:13:11,380 --> 00:13:14,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, I always figured you were no ordinary kid.</font>

282
00:13:14,750 --> 00:13:17,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But getting blessed and tested
by God is something else.</font>

283
00:13:20,290 --> 00:13:23,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It explains a lot, though.
Rodin must be beside himself.</font>

284
00:13:26,210 --> 00:13:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is your first time
trading for supplies, yeah?</font>

285
00:13:28,170 --> 00:13:30,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yes. Please show me the ropes.</font>

286
00:13:30,750 --> 00:13:33,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Good thing you stocked up on those albaheron, eh?</font>

287
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:35,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Seems like your boar hunt was fruitful, too!</font>

288
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:40,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Things go smoothly when it's just us serfs
and no commoners to muck it up!</font>

289
00:13:40,460 --> 00:13:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's the real difference
between serfs and commoners, anyway?</font>

290
00:13:44,750 --> 00:13:47,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, our social standing, for one.</font>

291
00:13:48,040 --> 00:13:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Also our taxes. The sixty percent rule
doesn't apply to commoners.</font>

292
00:13:53,170 --> 00:13:55,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They have what's called a "head tax" instead.</font>

293
00:13:55,040 --> 00:13:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They pay three gold coins for each adult
and one for each kid every year.</font>

294
00:13:59,420 --> 00:14:01,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, that's interesting.</font>

295
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:03,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And now, I slip in my real question...</font>

296
00:14:03,080 --> 00:14:06,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Is there any way for serfs to become commoners?</font>

297
00:14:06,380 --> 00:14:10,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There is. You gotta make a tribute
of 10 gold coins per person in the family.</font>

298
00:14:10,670 --> 00:14:14,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've also heard stories that the baron
can reward people with commoner status,</font>

299
00:14:14,880 --> 00:14:16,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">but I dunno if that's true or not.</font>

300
00:14:16,420 --> 00:14:18,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I see.</font>

301
00:14:18,750 --> 00:14:23,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My family's about to get a new member.
So it would cost us 50 gold coins, huh?</font>

302
00:14:30,170 --> 00:14:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm trading in five packs of boar jerky.</font>

303
00:14:38,670 --> 00:14:39,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, I'll do the same.</font>

304
00:14:40,540 --> 00:14:42,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'd like to trade in five packs
of albaheron jerky.</font>

305
00:14:47,920 --> 00:14:49,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Awesome!</font>

306
00:14:54,420 --> 00:14:55,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here ya go.</font>

307
00:14:59,210 --> 00:15:00,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa!</font>

308
00:15:02,040 --> 00:15:05,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One pack of jerky trades
for four days worth of firewood.</font>

309
00:15:05,880 --> 00:15:08,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Now that I know how bartering works,</font>

310
00:15:08,290 --> 00:15:10,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can do a bit of market research
next time I'm here.</font>

311
00:15:18,920 --> 00:15:20,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, sir.</font>

312
00:15:20,380 --> 00:15:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">May I ask how much
this would cost to buy with money?</font>

313
00:15:23,040 --> 00:15:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Five silver coins.</font>

314
00:15:24,580 --> 00:15:25,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thanks.</font>

315
00:15:25,960 --> 00:15:28,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Can't be a salt merchant without
a "salty" attitude, I guess.</font>

316
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:32,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What is that fruit hanging down over there?</font>

317
00:15:32,170 --> 00:15:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We call those "popos".</font>

318
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:37,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">They trade one-for-one with a bundle of your meat.</font>

319
00:15:37,210 --> 00:15:39,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Jeez, expensive! That's four times
the rate for molmos.</font>

320
00:15:39,960 --> 00:15:41,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You want one of those instead?</font>

321
00:15:41,250 --> 00:15:42,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No, sir! I'll keep these.</font>

322
00:15:46,750 --> 00:15:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A single bundle of albaheron jerky trades for:</font>

323
00:15:50,380 --> 00:15:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One bag of salt.</font>

324
00:15:51,830 --> 00:15:53,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Four molmo fruits.</font>

325
00:15:53,170 --> 00:15:54,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One popo fruit.</font>

326
00:15:54,460 --> 00:15:55,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Four days worth of firewood.</font>

327
00:15:56,330 --> 00:15:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The following forms of currency
have the same value:</font>

328
00:15:58,500 --> 00:16:00,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One gold coin. A hundred silver coins.</font>

329
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A thousand copper coins. Ten thousand iron coins.</font>

330
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:06,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">One bundle of jerky goes for one silver coin.</font>

331
00:16:06,710 --> 00:16:09,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">So saving up for 50 gold coins would mean...</font>

332
00:16:09,170 --> 00:16:11,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">hunting 500 albaherons.</font>

333
00:16:11,750 --> 00:16:14,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nice. That would only take a few years!</font>

334
00:16:14,210 --> 00:16:16,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">A walk in the park for a hardcore gamer like me!</font>

335
00:16:17,250 --> 00:16:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pardon me!</font>

336
00:16:19,380 --> 00:16:21,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do you have any medicines that recover MP?</font>

337
00:16:21,960 --> 00:16:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh?</font>

338
00:16:23,080 --> 00:16:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We don't carry anything that fancy 'round here.</font>

339
00:16:25,920 --> 00:16:27,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, really?</font>

340
00:16:27,380 --> 00:16:29,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Where are the healing medicines?</font>

341
00:16:29,130 --> 00:16:30,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Towards the back.</font>

342
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:36,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I wonder if my notebook can make drawings, too?</font>

343
00:16:39,210 --> 00:16:40,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh! It worked!</font>

344
00:16:40,960 --> 00:16:43,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It pays to try things out. Which reminds me...</font>

345
00:16:44,580 --> 00:16:47,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Excuse me, which of these is the muellerze flower?</font>

346
00:16:48,170 --> 00:16:51,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I don't have any of those!
And even if I did, I won't cut any deals for it!</font>

347
00:16:51,920 --> 00:16:53,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, I'm sorry.</font>

348
00:16:54,000 --> 00:16:58,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeesh. I'm still frustrated
over the last one I sold.</font>

349
00:16:58,380 --> 00:17:01,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Do you mean the one Mister Gerda
bought about a month ago?</font>

350
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:04,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, exactly! That darn Gerda fellow!</font>

351
00:17:04,330 --> 00:17:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He burst in here all of a sudden and demanded
my best medicine. He was beyond insistent!</font>

352
00:17:09,630 --> 00:17:11,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And so, you sold him a muellerze flower?</font>

353
00:17:11,710 --> 00:17:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Well, I happened to have one in stock that day.</font>

354
00:17:14,380 --> 00:17:16,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But when I told him it cost five gold coins,</font>

355
00:17:16,210 --> 00:17:18,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">he begged me to settle
for three and promised to pay later.</font>

356
00:17:18,500 --> 00:17:21,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He kept hollering about some friend needing help.
He even dropped to his hands and knees!</font>

357
00:17:22,000 --> 00:17:23,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Gerda's a real bro...</font>

358
00:17:23,750 --> 00:17:28,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Anyways, the guy was more persistent than a kid
at a candy store. I had to let him have it.</font>

359
00:17:28,880 --> 00:17:31,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But I was biting my nails like crazy
until he brought the money.</font>

360
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:34,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Still, it was a bad deal. I lost out in the end.</font>

361
00:17:34,210 --> 00:17:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">It really irks me!</font>

362
00:17:38,000 --> 00:17:39,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here. For you.</font>

363
00:17:40,080 --> 00:17:42,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh, sorry for going off like that!
You're here to trade, right?</font>

364
00:17:42,750 --> 00:17:44,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What would you like? Just let me know.</font>

365
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No. I'm giving this to you.</font>

366
00:17:47,380 --> 00:17:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Huh? What for?</font>

367
00:17:49,460 --> 00:17:54,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You did a great service selling that muellerze
flower at a discount. It saved my father's life.</font>

368
00:17:54,880 --> 00:17:55,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh my...</font>

369
00:17:56,080 --> 00:17:58,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is a token of my appreciation.
I'll bring more next time!</font>

370
00:17:59,330 --> 00:18:00,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Thank you, sir.</font>

371
00:18:00,710 --> 00:18:02,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Aw, don't mention it.</font>

372
00:18:06,170 --> 00:18:10,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Holy crap! Just one of those
costs 50 silver coins?!</font>

373
00:18:10,040 --> 00:18:11,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's five albaherons...</font>

374
00:18:13,540 --> 00:18:14,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey!</font>

375
00:18:15,130 --> 00:18:17,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whatchu want with my family's shop, dirthead?</font>

376
00:18:17,790 --> 00:18:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This joker again.
Guess his dad is a blacksmith, huh?</font>

377
00:18:22,080 --> 00:18:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">That's the chieftain's son hanging out with him.</font>

378
00:18:24,580 --> 00:18:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Nothing in particular. Bye.</font>

379
00:18:28,250 --> 00:18:29,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Take this!</font>

380
00:18:29,750 --> 00:18:30,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What was that for?!</font>

381
00:18:30,960 --> 00:18:33,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You only get to pass if you agree to be my minion!</font>

382
00:18:34,670 --> 00:18:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Who does he think he is,
a player killer in an MMO?</font>

383
00:18:36,880 --> 00:18:40,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">PVP doesn't score any EXP,
so I usually never bother with it.</font>

384
00:18:44,460 --> 00:18:46,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's wrong? You chicken out already?</font>

385
00:18:47,080 --> 00:18:49,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Th-that's not fair!</font>

386
00:18:49,040 --> 00:18:51,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You think that excuse will work
on the battlefield?</font>

387
00:18:51,630 --> 00:18:53,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Mister tough guy.</font>

388
00:18:54,790 --> 00:18:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Go grab whatever weapon you want.
I'll wait right here.</font>

389
00:18:58,920 --> 00:19:02,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Fine! You better not run, punk!</font>

390
00:19:02,380 --> 00:19:04,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Keep an eye on him, Pelmoas!</font>

391
00:19:06,080 --> 00:19:07,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hi there, Pelmoas.</font>

392
00:19:08,040 --> 00:19:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Uh, hey, Allen.</font>

393
00:19:12,170 --> 00:19:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll give you some credit!</font>

394
00:19:13,750 --> 00:19:15,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You had the balls to stick around!</font>

395
00:19:16,330 --> 00:19:17,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Whoa, whoa, whoa.</font>

396
00:19:18,080 --> 00:19:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Cheap move!</font>

397
00:19:24,830 --> 00:19:27,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">His attacks hit pretty hard.
Makes sense for an Axe User.</font>

398
00:19:28,130 --> 00:19:31,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But he hardly compares
to the three-star power of Krena.</font>

399
00:19:32,960 --> 00:19:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">What's the big idea? Come at me, already!</font>

400
00:19:43,960 --> 00:19:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dogora, Knight of the Axe.</font>

401
00:19:47,460 --> 00:19:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'll be back to trade at your store someday.</font>

402
00:19:52,330 --> 00:19:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">See ya.</font>

403
00:19:54,000 --> 00:19:56,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dammit!</font>

404
00:20:06,080 --> 00:20:08,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Feast your eyes. I'm back in tip-top shape!</font>

405
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:11,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Just don't pull a muscle by overexerting yourself.</font>

406
00:20:11,580 --> 00:20:12,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Right!</font>

407
00:20:12,880 --> 00:20:16,380
<font size="27"><b>{\an7}AT KRENA'S HOUSE</b></font>

408
00:20:18,380 --> 00:20:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ow!</font>

409
00:20:19,420 --> 00:20:23,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">When will you learn, Dogora?
I told you to anticipate my moves.</font>

410
00:20:23,210 --> 00:20:24,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, I know!</font>

411
00:20:25,040 --> 00:20:28,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Why can't I land a hit, dammit?!</font>

412
00:20:30,420 --> 00:20:31,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hiyah!</font>

413
00:20:33,500 --> 00:20:36,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I can tell Krena's taking it super easy on him.</font>

414
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:39,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But Mash is doing pretty good, actually.</font>

415
00:20:39,290 --> 00:20:41,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">He might have the talent of a Spear User!</font>

416
00:20:41,880 --> 00:20:43,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're wide open!</font>

417
00:20:44,000 --> 00:20:44,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ouch!</font>

418
00:20:45,460 --> 00:20:48,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Big brudder! I like this thing!</font>

419
00:20:48,290 --> 00:20:50,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Oh yeah? That's great!</font>

420
00:20:50,630 --> 00:20:53,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm excited to see how
your Appraisal Ceremony will go in two years!</font>

421
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:55,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Dammit! I'm not done yet!</font>

422
00:21:02,420 --> 00:21:04,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Wow, Myulla is so cute!</font>

423
00:21:05,920 --> 00:21:08,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">There was a time you were this cute, too.</font>

424
00:21:08,380 --> 00:21:10,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">My own little prince charming.</font>

425
00:21:10,920 --> 00:21:12,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Shucks...</font>

426
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:14,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I'm back.</font>

427
00:21:14,420 --> 00:21:15,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Welcome home!</font>

428
00:21:16,790 --> 00:21:18,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">You're later than usual.</font>

429
00:21:18,880 --> 00:21:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And Mister Gerda's with you?</font>

430
00:21:21,040 --> 00:21:22,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We were summoned by the chieftain.</font>

431
00:21:25,920 --> 00:21:27,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Here's the deal.</font>

432
00:21:27,460 --> 00:21:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The cheftain wants us to raise the number of boars
that we deliver to the baron from 10 to 15.</font>

433
00:21:34,630 --> 00:21:38,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And to make that happen, he expects us to let
the commoners join the hunt again this year.</font>

434
00:21:39,000 --> 00:21:42,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Ridiculous! After you suffered that awful injury?!</font>

435
00:21:42,380 --> 00:21:44,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We wanted to say no, of course.</font>

436
00:21:44,540 --> 00:21:47,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But this order came directly
from the baron, apparently.</font>

437
00:21:47,750 --> 00:21:50,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">If we don't deliver 15 boars by winter this year,</font>

438
00:21:50,420 --> 00:21:52,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">they're going to recruit
more serfs from elsewhere.</font>

439
00:21:53,540 --> 00:21:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">More serfs in the village
results in less land to go around.</font>

440
00:21:59,080 --> 00:22:03,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Which means that serfs who can't hunt
might have their land taken away from them.</font>

441
00:22:03,580 --> 00:22:07,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">And that risks changing
the very nature of Krena Village.</font>

442
00:22:08,420 --> 00:22:11,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Worse yet, they want us
to hunt 20 boars next year.</font>

443
00:22:11,170 --> 00:22:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No way! That's impossible!</font>

444
00:22:13,630 --> 00:22:18,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The only way to make it happen is for us to hunt
more often than the usual once every ten days.</font>

445
00:22:18,000 --> 00:22:21,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">But that just means greater risks
for everyone involved!</font>

446
00:22:21,290 --> 00:22:25,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The opinions of a few serfs can't compete
with the orders of the baron.</font>

447
00:22:25,500 --> 00:22:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">No matter how unfair it seems.</font>

448
00:22:27,000 --> 00:22:28,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">This is awful!</font>

449
00:22:28,580 --> 00:22:31,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah, it's not fair. But...</font>

450
00:22:31,830 --> 00:22:33,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">We don't have the luxury of choice.</font>

451
00:22:33,960 --> 00:22:36,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Okay, let's say that you
increase the number of hunts.</font>

452
00:22:37,040 --> 00:22:41,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then they'll just keep expecting more from you
over the years, until it soon becomes impossible.</font>

453
00:22:42,040 --> 00:22:44,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">The ultimate result is still
recruiting more serfs, right?</font>

454
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Hey, Allen. Don't interupt when the adults are-</font>

455
00:22:48,250 --> 00:22:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Yeah. You make a good point.</font>

456
00:22:50,880 --> 00:22:54,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Are you suggesting we do what the chieftain says
and let commoners join the hunt again?</font>

457
00:22:55,130 --> 00:22:56,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Pretty much.</font>

458
00:22:56,210 --> 00:22:56,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Out of the question!</font>

459
00:22:56,960 --> 00:22:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Those fools are nothing but dead weight!</font>

460
00:22:59,330 --> 00:23:01,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Then you have to find a way to make them useful.</font>

461
00:23:02,500 --> 00:23:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Listen. I have wisdom
that was blessed to me by Lord Elmea.</font>

462
00:23:07,330 --> 00:23:09,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I've spent countless hours across numerous games,</font>

463
00:23:09,750 --> 00:23:12,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">making characters as strong
as they could possibly be.</font>

464
00:23:13,080 --> 00:23:14,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Both flying solo and in pairs.</font>

465
00:23:14,790 --> 00:23:18,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I know how to integrate a newbie into a party
so they can safely gain the necessary EXP.</font>

466
00:23:19,830 --> 00:23:22,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">Will you let me handle all this?</font>

467
00:23:23,460 --> 00:23:25,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="52">I think I know how to make it work.</font>

